locality: Vietnam, Lao Cai Province, Van Ban Nature Reserve, east slope of the Hoang Lien Son Range, east of road QL 279.
Van Ban District, Khanh Yen Ha municipality, to the S of Na Nheo village. (FFI Project.)

Vi Xuyen district, Cao Bo municipality, Tam Ve village. Collections from below 1750 m to 1300 m; along ridge just S of camp; in semi-closed; mixed evergreen; semi-deciduous forest with thick undergrowth at lower elevation and along stream to open undergrowth with dead bamboo; upper elevation very steep intergrading into lower montane, wetter forests - some rocky outcrops; somewhat disturbed due to clearing and logging. On deep humus-rich soil and decaying quartz rock; GPS reading not taken, coordinates only approximate.
